---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Free online tools for SEO, finance, development, and more. Mortgage calculator, ROI calculator, JSON formatter, password generator, and 20+ other tools. No signup required.">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Free Online Web Tools</h1>
    <p>23 free tools for finance, SEO, development, and everyday calculations. No signup, no limits, no hassle.</p>
  </section>
  
  <div class="filter-bar">
    <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterTools('all')">All</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Finance')">💰 Finance</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('SEO')">🔍 SEO</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Developer')">💻 Developer</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Utility')">🛠️ Utility</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Writing')">✍️ Writing</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Design')">🎨 Design</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Health')">💪 Health</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Shopping')">🛒 Shopping</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Security')">🔒 Security</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterTools('Math')">🔢 Math</button>
  </div>
  
  <div class="tools-grid">
    {tools.map((tool) => (
      <a href={`/${tool.slug}`} class="tool-card" data-tag={tool.tag}>
        <div class="icon">{tool.icon}</div>
        <h3>{tool.title}</h3>
        <p>{tool.description}</p>
        <span class="tag">{tool.tag}</span>
      </a>
    ))}
  </div>
  
  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Why ToolMixr?</h2>
    <p>All tools run entirely in your browser — nothing is sent to a server. Your data stays private, always.</p>
    <p>No accounts, no signups, no paywalls. Every tool is 100% free to use, with no hidden limits.</p>
    <p>Built for speed. Tools load instantly and work on any device — desktop, tablet, or phone.</p>
    <p>Finance tools that help you plan. Mortgage, ROI, compound interest, and crypto calculators — all free, all private.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
